val encounterSelect = sqlContext.sql("""
  SELECT
    recordId as encounterId,
    parent as personId,
    admit_date as admitDate,
    facility.code as facility,
    service_category as serviceCategory,
    row_number() over (partition by parent order by admit_date asc, recordId asc) as enc_seq ,
    row_number() over (partition by parent order by admit_date asc, recordId asc) -1 as enc_prev,
    row_number() over (partition by parent,service_category order by admit_date asc, recordId asc) as enc_seq_sc,
    row_number() over (partition by parent,service_category order by admit_date asc, recordId asc) -1 as enc_prev_sc,
    row_number() over (partition by parent,facility.code order by admit_date asc, recordId asc) as enc_seq_f,
    row_number() over (partition by parent,facility.code order by admit_date asc, recordId asc) -1 as enc_prev_f,
    cast(null as integer) as yearsBetween,
    cast(null as integer) as yearsBetween_sc,
    cast(null as integer) as yearsBetween_not_sc,
    cast(null as integer) as yearsBetween_f,
    cast(null as integer) as yearsBetween_not_f,
    cast(null as integer) as yearsBetween_f_or_sc
    FROM encountersES
    order by parent, admit_date
""")
encounterSelect.createOrReplaceTempView("encounter")

val encounterYearsBetween = sqlContext.sql("""
select cur.encounterId,
case when prv.personid is null then 99 else datediff(cur.admitDate,prv.admitDate)/365.25 end as yearsBetween,
case when prv_f.personid is null then 99 else datediff(cur.admitDate,prv_f.admitDate)/365.25 end as yearsBetween_f,
case when prv_sc.personid is null then 99 else datediff(cur.admitDate,prv_sc.admitDate)/365.25 end as yearsBetween_sc
from encounter cur 
left join encounter prv on cur.personid = prv.personid and cur.enc_prev = prv.enc_seq
left join encounter prv_f on cur.personid = prv_f.personid and cur.enc_prev_f = prv_f.enc_seq_f and cur.facility = prv_f.facility
left join encounter prv_sc on cur.personid = prv_sc.personid and cur.enc_prev_sc = prv_sc.enc_seq_sc and cur.serviceCategory = prv_sc.serviceCategory
""")

val attributableEncounters = sqlContext.sql("""
  SELECT
    encounter.recordId AS encounter_id,
    admit_date,
    person_id,
    campaign,
    first_contact,
    last_contact,
    contact_count,
    datediff(admit_date, last_contact) as days_after_last_contact,
    -- TODO: Add a UDF for more precise values
    datediff(admit_date, last_contact)/30.44 AS months_after_last_contact,
    datediff(admit_date, first_contact) as days_after_first_contact,
    datediff(admit_date, first_contact)/30.44 AS months_after_first_contact
  FROM encounter INNER JOIN campaign_activity_summary ON encounter.parent = campaign_activity_summary.person_id
  WHERE
    admit_date >= first_contact
    AND admit_date <= add_months(last_contact, 12)
""")

attributableEncounters.show()
println(s"${attributableEncounters.count} encounters attributed out of ${encounters.count} total encounters")

case class EncounterActivityUpdate(
    campaign_name: String,
    days_after_first_contact: Integer,
    months_after_first_contact: BigDecimal,
    days_after_last_contact: Integer,
    months_after_last_contact: BigDecimal,
    contact_count: Long
)

val updates = attributableEncounters
  .rdd
  .map(e => (
      Map(
          ID -> s"""${e.getAs[String]("encounter_id")}_${e.getAs[String]("campaign").replaceAll("\\s", "_")}""".toString(),
          PARENT -> e.getAs[String]("encounter_id"),
          ROUTING -> e.getAs[String]("person_id")

      EncounterActivityUpdate(
          e.getAs[String]("campaign"),
          e.getAs[Integer]("days_after_first_contact"),
          e.getAs[java.math.BigDecimal]("months_after_first_contact"),
          e.getAs[Integer]("days_after_last_contact"),
          e.getAs[java.math.BigDecimal]("months_after_last_contact"),
          e.getAs[Long]("contact_count")
      )
    )
  )
